Siesta tutorial material.

Bases: Examples of generation of basis sets and KB projectors.

Pseudo: The pseudopotential generation examples are in the Atom program
        distribution (Pseudo/atom/Tutorial from the top directory of
        the Siesta distribution).

See also the Tests directory at the top of the Siesta distribution for
examples.
